explicitJournal в†ђ ctx.ResolveArithmeticCurrencyProof ProofSnapshot вџЁвџЁLine вџЁ"2026-06-15", "memo", "assets:bank", "expenses:food", "100", "currency=JPY"вџ©вџ©, вџЁвџ©, вџЁвџ©вџ©
