explicitBudget в†ђ ctx.ResolveArithmeticCurrencyProof ProofSnapshot вџЁвџЁLine вџЁ"2026-06-15", "memo", "assets:bank", "expenses:food", "100"вџ©вџ©, вџЁвџ©, вџЁLine вџЁ"2026-06-16", "budget", "assets:bank", "budget:food", "20", "currency="вџ©вџ©вџ©
